Tk/LineNumberText version 0.5
=============================

Add line numbers to your favourite Text-derived widget.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Tk

